io.confluent.ksql.execution.plan

Interface ExecutionKeyFactory<K>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of the key, usually either GenericKey or Windowed<GenericKey>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExecutionKeyFactory.UnwindowedFactory, ExecutionKeyFactory.WindowedFactory

    public interface ExecutionKeyFactory<K>
    The ExecutionKeyFactory is in charge of creating the keys and the Serdes for the keys of any particular execution step.
